                        <em>Electronic</em>. For each low mass emissions unit, report the results of the analysis performed to qualify as a low mass emissions unit under <a href="~/Part75/75.19" style="text-decoration: none">§75.19</a>(c). This report will include either the previous three years actual or projected emissions. The following items should be included:
