                        </ol>
                    </li>
                </ol>
            </li>
            <li> For each gas-fired unit the designated representative shall include in the monitoring plan, in electronic format, the following: current calendar year, fuel usage data as specified in the definition of gas-fired in §72.2 of this part, and an indication of whether the data are actual or projected data.</li>
