    </li>
    <li>
        <em>Contents of the Monitoring Plan</em>. The requirements of paragraphs (g) and (h) of this section shall be met on and after January 1, 2009. Notwithstanding this requirement, the provisions of paragraphs (g) and (h) of this section may be implemented prior to January 1, 2009, as follows. In 2008, the owner or operator may opt to record and report the monitoring plan information in paragraphs (g) and (h) of this section, in lieu of recording and reporting the information in paragraphs (e) and (f) of this section. Each monitoring plan shall contain the information in paragraph (g)(1) of this section in electronic format and the information in paragraph (g)(2) of this section in hard copy format. Electronic storage of all monitoring plan information, including the hard copy portions, is permissible provided that a paper copy of the information can be furnished upon request for audit purposes.
        <ol>
            <li>
                <em>Electronic</em>.
                <ol type="i">
                    <li>
